OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,FThe MP for West Lancashire has stepped
OL,7,Fdown from her role as health minister,
OL,8,Fas she undergoes chemotherapy.
OL,10,FIn a post on X, Ashley Dalton, who has
OL,11,Fadvanced breast cancer, said that she
OL,12,Fwants to be able to focus on
OL,13,Frepresenting members of her
OL,14,Fconstituency while she continues her
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
