OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,FThe MP, who is the Parliamentary Under-
OL,7,FSecretary of State for Public Health
OL,8,Fand Prevention in the Department of
OL,9,FHealth and Social Care, said: "I have
OL,10,Ftaken the decision to step down from
OL,11,Fmy ministerial responsibilities to
OL,12,Fallow me to focus on my job
OL,13,Frepresenting you, the people of West
OL,14,FLancashire, while I continue to
OL,15,Freceive oral chemotherapy treatment."
OL,17,FThe Labour MP was first diagnosed with
OL,18,Fbreast cancer in 2014 and underwent
OL,19,Fsurgery, chemotherapy and radiotherapy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,FShe was then diagnosed with breast
OL,7,Fcancer for the second time in January
OL,8,Flast year.
OL,10,FIn a letter addressed to Prime
OL,11,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer, Ashley
OL,12,Fsaid: "Last month I had the privilege
OL,13,Fof introducing the Government's
OL,14,Fnational cancer plan to parliament.
OL,16,F"As a woman living with and receiving
OL,17,Ftreatment for static breast cancer
OL,18,Fbeing trusted with writing this plan
OL,19,Fhas been an immense honour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,F"The national Council plan won't only
OL,7,Fsay 320,000 lives over its lifetime,
OL,8,Fit will help people living with cancer
OL,9,Fto live well, and to work well.
OL,11,F"As I was stood at the dispatch box
OL,12,Fspeaking about the difference this
OL,13,Fwork will make the lives of people
OL,14,Flike me up and down the country, I
OL,15,Freflected on what living and working
OL,16,Fwell means for myself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
