PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,F"Your government has committed to
OL,7,Fmaking sure that people with long-term
OL,8,Fhealth conditions are supported and
OL,9,Funable to return to or continue to
OL,10,Fwork where they can.
OL,12,F"It is also so important that we
OL,13,Frecognise the value of all of us to
OL,14,Fcontribute and participate and that we
OL,15,Fstop writing people off due to health
OL,16,For disability.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,F"My constituents deserve a member of
OL,7,Fparliament to represent them with
OL,8,Fdiligence and conviction whilst my
OL,9,Foral chemotherapy treatment will not
OL,10,Fstop me from being that champion for
OL,11,FWest Lancashire, I believe now is the
OL,12,Fright time to make the reasonable
OL,13,Fadjustments.
OL,15,F"I need to both manage my condition
OL,16,Fand focus on being a constituency MP
OL,17,Fby stepping back from ministerial
OL,18,Fduties."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,FShe continued: "I will be forever
OL,7,Fgrateful for the confidence you have
OL,8,Fshown me, inviting me to bring my
OL,9,Fexperience into government people
OL,10,Fliving with cancer know that the
OL,11,Fgovernment placed cancer patient
OL,12,Fpatients at the heart of the national
OL,13,Fcouncil plan because you put a cancer
OL,14,Fpatient at the head of the plan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
