PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,F"It is with great pride that I also
OL,7,Fled the HIV action plan and the men's
OL,8,Fhealth strategy which we have launched
OL,9,Fduring my time at the department of
OL,10,Fhealth and social care these three
OL,11,Flandmark plans we have delivered in
OL,12,Fthe past 12 months will be
OL,13,Ftransformational for people across
OL,14,FCountry.
OL,16,F"I returned to the back benches
OL,17,Fcommitted to being a powerful voice in
OL,18,FWestminster for my constituents.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
