CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772463772
OL,3,CWest Lancashire MP steps down from
OL,4,Cministerial role for cancer treatment
OL,6,F"I will continue to work towards
OL,7,Fimproving health outcomes for people
OL,8,Fliving with cancer and support your
OL,9,Fleadership on the Government agenda to
OL,10,Fbring about the change the country
OL,11,Ftrusted us to deliver."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
